Package: planktonr
Title: Analysis and Visualisation of Plankton Data
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jason D.", "Everett", , "jase.everett@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6681-8054")),
    person("Claire H.", "Davies", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0424-1835"))
  )
Description: Facilitates access, analysis, and visualisation of phytoplankton, 
    zooplankton, and biogeochemical data from the Integrated Marine Observing 
    System (IMOS). Provides functions to download data from the Australian Ocean 
    Data Network (AODN), calculate ecological indices, perform trend analysis, 
    and create publication-ready visualisations. Primary data sources include 
    the National Reference Stations (NRS) network, Continuous Plankton Recorder 
    (CPR) survey, and Southern Ocean Time Series (SOTS).
